'''艾伯特·雷納德·羅森'''（{{lang-en|Albert Leonard Rosen}}，{{bd|1924年|2月29日|2015年|3月13日|}}），綽號「Flip」和「希伯來大槌」，為美國職棒大聯盟的三壘手。他整個職業生涯都效力於印地安人隊。
==職業生涯==
1947年，23歲的羅森登上大聯盟。1948年，羅森主要都待在小聯盟，他這年只上場5場比賽。1948年世界大賽，羅森主要擔任三壘手Ken Keltner的替補。<ref>{{cite news|title=Rosen and 24 Other Indians Are Ruled Eligible To COmpete In World Series|work=[[The_Plain_Dealer|The Plain Dealer]]|date=1948-09-29|page=26}}</ref>1950年，Keltner被交易到紅襪，羅森也成為球隊的主戰三壘手。這年他還敲出37轟，一度豎下了美聯菜鳥的單季全壘打紀錄。<ref>''Great Baseball Feats, Facts and Figures'', 2008 Edition, p.346, David Nemec and Scott Flatow, A Signet Book, Penguin Group, New York; {{ISBN|978-0-451-22363-0}}</ref>這項紀錄一直到1987年才被[[馬克·麥奎爾|馬克·麥奎爾]]打破。<ref>{{cite web|agency=Associated Press Archive|title=Baseball Today|url=http://docs.newsbank.com/g/GooglePM/APAB/lib00581,122CA98E1CEF7498.html|date=2008-08-10|access-date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120708140841/http://docs.newsbank.com/g/GooglePM/APAB/lib00581,122CA98E1CEF7498.html|archive-date=2012-07-08}}</ref>而他在6月時還締造連四場比賽開轟的紀錄，寫下了印地安人菜鳥的紀錄。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2011/08/jason_kipnis_on_a_hr_roll_clev.html |accessdate=2012-11-04 |location=Cleveland, Ohio |date=2011-08-04 |work=[[The_Plain_Dealer|The Plain Dealer]] |title=Jason Kipnis on a HR roll: Cleveland Indians daily briefing |first=Paul |last=Hoynes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014231618/http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2011/08/jason_kipnis_on_a_hr_roll_clev.html |archivedate=2012-10-14 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2011/08/jason_kipnis_on_a_hr_roll_clev.html] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014231618/http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2011/08/jason_kipnis_on_a_hr_roll_clev.html |date=2012-10-14 }}</ref>這年他的打擊率為2成87，並打回116分打點。另外他還獲得100次保送，成為美聯單季獲得最多保送的菜鳥球員。<ref name="docstoc.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.docstoc.com/docs/2505908/Cleveland-Indians-RecordsHistory|accessdate=2012-11-01|title=Cleveland Indians Records/History|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701174121/http://www.docstoc.com/docs/2505908/Cleveland-Indians-RecordsHistory|dead-url=no}}</ref>這項紀錄也一直到2017年才被[[亞倫·賈吉|亞倫·賈吉]]打破。儘管他拿下全壘打王，不過他在MVP票選上只有拿下17名。

1951年，羅森全勤出賽。該年他的打擊率為2成65，並敲出24轟與102分打點。這季他還敲出4支滿貫全壘打，這個紀錄直到2006年才被[[崔維斯·哈夫納|崔維斯·哈夫納]]以單季5支滿貫砲給打破。<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=[[Reading_Eagle|Reading Eagle]]|date=2006-07-08|accessdate=2012-11-01|title=Hafner hits record fifth grand slam|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LGMxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MqIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2697,3287400&dq=al-rosen+record&hl=en|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107114407/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LGMxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MqIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2697,3287400&dq=al-rosen+record&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1952年，羅森以單季105分打點拿下打點王，另外他297個壘打數也是聯盟第一。這年他的打擊率為3成02，並敲出28轟。4月29日，羅森達成單場敲出3支全壘打的成就。<ref name="docstoc.com"/>這項隊史紀錄一直到1959年6月10日才被[[洛基·柯拉維托|洛基·柯拉維托]]超越。這年他在MVP票選上拿下第10名。

1953年可說是羅森的生涯年，這年他的打擊率高達3成36，並敲出43轟與145分打點拿下全壘打王和打點王。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/leaders_bat_50_season.shtml|title=Cleveland Indians Top 50 Single-Season Batting Leaders - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|accessdate=2017-09-20|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031040101/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CLE/leaders_bat_50_season.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他這年還達成連續20場比賽敲出安打的成就。<ref name="docstoc.com"/>在防守方面，羅森也表現得很出色，他這年一共製造38次雙殺和338次助殺。羅森在這年差一點就能拿下打擊三冠王，<ref name=warsinskey>{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2013/09/cleveland_indians_infielder_al.html|title=Cleveland Indians infielder Al Rosen's quest for baseball's 1953 Triple Crown went down to the wire 60 years ago Friday|accessdate=2013-09-27|first=Tim|last=Warsinskey|publisher=Cleveland Plain Dealer ([[cleveland.com|cleveland.com]])|date=2013-09-26|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018131849/http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2013/09/cleveland_indians_infielder_al.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他最後拿下了MVP。

棒球數據專家Bill James認為這年羅森的表現是大聯盟史上任何一位三壘手繳出的單季最佳表現。<ref>Baseball-Reference.com [https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_season.shtml Single-Season Leaders & Records for Wins Above Replacement] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_season.shtml |date=20210418181154 }}</ref><ref>Baseball-Reference.com [https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_bat_season.shtml] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_bat_season.shtml |date=20210503034618 }} Single-Season Leaders & Records for WAR Position Players</ref>

1954年，羅森的打擊率剛好3成，並敲出24轟與102分打點。這年明星賽羅森帶傷上陣，結果他還敲出了2支全壘打，他也成為了明星賽的MVP。他在明星賽拿下5分打點追平了[[泰德·威廉斯|泰德·威廉斯]]先前的紀錄，而這項紀錄之後再也無人能追平或超越。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110711&content_id=21737670&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |accessdate=2012-11-01 |title=Fascinating facts about the All-Star Game |first=Roger |last=Schlueter |publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |date=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023120050/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110711&content_id=21737670&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>

名人堂傳奇教頭Casey Stangel曾給予羅森高度讚賞，他認為羅森是一名很努力的球員，並隨時能在場上給對手致命一擊。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,858499,00.html |title=Sport: Top of the League |work=[[TIME|TIME]] |date=1954-07-05 |accessdate=2010-04-09 |archive-date=2009-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905064904/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,858499,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>1954年，印地安人再次闖進世界大賽，不過最後遭到橫掃出局。羅森的薪水也在隔年被減了5000美元。

1955年，羅森的打擊率下滑到2成44，並敲出21轟與81分打點。隔年更是因為背傷和腿傷，使得他才32歲就在球季結束後宣布告別棒球賽場。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thebaseballpage.com/players/rosenal01.php |title=Al Rosen Facts from |publisher=The Baseball Page.com |accessdate=2010-04-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101221051412/http://www.thebaseballpage.com/players/rosenal01.php |archivedate=2010-12-21 }}</ref>
==個人生活==
退休後，羅森轉行成為證券經紀人，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.historicbaseball.com/players/r/rosen_al.html|title=Al Rosen – Exploded on the scene in the AL|publisher=Historicbaseball.com|accessdate=2010-04-09|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104102434/http://www.historicbaseball.com/players/r/rosen_al.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並且一當就是20多年。<ref name=Chron>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/08/sports/baseball/08steinbrenner.html|accessdate=2012-11-04|date=2010-05-07|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|title=Chronicling Steinbrenner and His Turbulent Tenure|first=Richard|last=Sandomir|authorlink=Richard Sandomir|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108170559/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/08/sports/baseball/08steinbrenner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1978年至1979年，羅森成為洋基隊的主席。<ref name=Chron/>1980年至1985年，他成為太空人隊的主席。1985年至1992年，他還擔任巨人隊的總經理。這對期間他幫助巨人從墊底的球隊搖身一變成為奪冠勁旅，這也使得他曾拿下國聯年度最佳總經理獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Al_Rosen_1924 |title=Al Rosen profile at |publisher=BaseballLibrary.com |accessdate=2010-04-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604105218/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/ballplayers/player.php?name=Al_Rosen_1924 |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref>

1971年5月，羅森的第一任妻子過世。後來羅森再婚並育有三子。2015年3月13日，羅森因病去世，享壽91歲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/112723684/al-rosen-the-1953-al-mvp-with-indians-and-an-executive-for-yankees-astros-and-giants |title=Rosen, 1953 MVP and four-time All-Star, dies at 91 |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date= |website= |publisher=mlb.com |accessdate=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2017-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144510/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/112723684/al-rosen-the-1953-al-mvp-with-indians-and-an-executive-for-yankees-astros-and-giants/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/mvp-yankee-exec-al-rosen-dies-91-article-1.2149520|title=Former MVP, Yankee exec Al Rosen dies at 91|publisher=|accessdate=2017-09-20|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630122157/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/mvp-yankee-exec-al-rosen-dies-91-article-1.2149520|dead-url=no}}</ref>
